</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Harry Potter: Flying Lesson</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In the Harry Potter video games, Harry was required to fly his broom through a series of hoops in order to pass the flying class </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PassThroughTheRings" class='trope-example-link'>Pass Through the Rings</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
